content.html: A general strike has been called across France tomorrow. It’s worth repeating that while the riots are eye catching, it’s this power to act collectively, and to withhold labor collectively, that we need to learn from. Solidarity with the workers of France.
content.value:
A general strike has been called across France tomorrow.

It’s worth repeating that while the riots are eye catching, it’s this power to act collectively, and to withhold labor collectively, that we need to learn from.

Solidarity with the workers of France.
